  "title": "A big round metallic UFO sighted in Cabo de Santo Agostinho-PE [1999]",
  "URL": "http://brazilianufoarchives.com/2020/06/16/a-big-round-metallic-ufo-sighted-in-cabo-de-santo-agostinho-pe-1999/",
  "short_URL": "https://wp.me/pc3ctW-ug",
  "content": "<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>OCT 14th, 1999</strong>. Time: 01:40pm. In Cabo de Santo Agostinho, State of Pernambuco, a witness spotted a shiny metallic UFO with a round shape, similar to the &#8220;new moon&#8221;. According to the witness, the unknown object was &#8220;very large&#8221; in size and flew horizontally at high speed [&#8220;jets speed&#8221;] going from the Southeast towards the ocean. Also according to the sighting reported to COMDABRA [Brazilian Aerospace Defense Command], the witness stated: &#8220;It could be an object in the form of a plate maneuvering (as if standing on its side).&#8221;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>Cf.</em> ARQUIVO NACIONAL (Brasil). Sistema de Informações do Arquivo Nacional (SIAN). Fundo ‘Objeto Voador Não Identificado (OVNI)’. Código de Referência BR DFANBSB ARX.0.0.562. “</span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">Avistamento de objeto voador não identificado na região de Pontezinha, Cabo de Santo Agostinho, Pernambuco”. Brasília, DF. 1952 a 2015. Último acesso realizado em 27/05/2020.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">The BRAZILIAN UFO ARCHIVES website is a private initiative and IS NOT endorsed or sponsored by the Arquivo Nacional do Brasil [see our ‘Info’ page]. </span></em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>*THE ORIGINAL FILE WITH THE CASE REFERRED TO IN THIS TEXT CAN BE FOUND IN THE DOCUMENTAL COLLECTION OF “ARQUIVO NACIONAL DO BRASIL, LOCATED IN THE “OBJETO VOADOR NÃO IDENTIFICADO (OVNI)” FUND, UNDER THE REFERENCE CODE [“Código de Referência”] MENTIONED ABOVE.</em> <strong><a style=\"color:#808000;\" href=\"http://sian.an.gov.br/sianex/consulta/login.asp\">HERE IS THE LINK TO SEARCH THEIR WEBSITE</a></strong></span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"> </span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n",
